invalid type: string "### Silver Plan\n- **Liability Coverage**: Up to $100,000 for bodily injury and $50,000 for property damage.\n- **Collision Deductible**: $500.\n- **Comprehensive Deductible**: $500.\n- **Roadside Assistance**: Included (limit 3 events per year).\n- **Windshield Replacement**: Included with $50 deductible.\n- **Rental Reimbursement**: Up to $30/day for max 30 days.", expected